data.description: SELLERS OFFERING $5,000 TOWARD BUYER CLOSING COSTS This lovingly updated home in a gated community is waiting for you.  You'll find luxury vinyl tile throughout the downstairs with carpet only in the three upstairs bedrooms.  Solar screens added to all windows help keep those hot summer electric bills down, and the full in-ground sprinkler system will keep the yard well hydrated in the hottest times. One living area downstairs and one upstairs, two dining areas, a large pantry and all bedrooms upstairs allow for great living space throughout the home. Updated light fixtures, kitchen sink and faucet and more are just some of the features that have been added to this home.
